<div class="QandA grid-item secondaried">
    <h4 class="Q">
        Q: Can I drink alcohol? <img class="faqarrow"
            src="https://www.flaticon.com/svg/static/icons/svg/892/892499.svg">
    </h4>
    <p class="A">A: You can, but it's not going to help. Alcohol negatively affects diet, training and nutrition,
        so it will slow your progress. It's also more calorific than you think, at 7kcal per gram. Protein and
        carbs are 4 calories per gram each, for reference.
    </p>
    <p class="A">Again, moderation is key. Don't overdo it, and plan your rest days to be the day after that big
        party.
    </p>
